    <item>
      <title>法国总理面临预算纠纷的危险：值得关注的事项</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/france-s-premier-risks-turmoil-in-budget-showdown-what-to-watch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总理弗朗索瓦·贝鲁周一面临一场成败攸关的考验，他计划在不经议会投票的情况下推动新预算获得批准，这一危险过程可能会导致法国在不到一年的时间内第三届政府垮台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/france-s-premier-risks-turmoil-in-budget-showdown-what-to-watch</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚亿万富翁在选举前向政党注入资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/gina-rinehart-s-firm-triples-its-australia-center-right-donation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚首富吉娜·莱因哈特 (Gina Rinehart) 在最新的政治捐款数据显示，她对中右翼反对党自由国家党 (Liberal National) 的捐款增加了 200% 以上，因为该国的亿万富翁在 5 月 17 日举行的全国大选之前对两大政党都下了大赌注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/gina-rinehart-s-firm-triples-its-australia-center-right-donation</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 03:04:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普加大对欧盟的关税威胁，计划与加拿大、墨西哥通话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trump-says-tariffs-will-definitely-happen-with-european-union</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普加大了对欧盟的关税威胁，同时表示他将与加拿大和墨西哥领导人进行会谈。在贸易战前景变成现实的忙碌周末过后，股市下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trump-says-tariffs-will-definitely-happen-with-european-union</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 00:41:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克称 DOGE 将停止向美国承包商支付国库款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/musk-says-doge-is-rapidly-shutting-down-treasury-payments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克表示，他的政府效率执法者“DOGE 团队”正在停止向联邦承包商支付部分款项，这表明这位世界首富可能有权访问美国财政部使用的敏感系统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/musk-says-doge-is-rapidly-shutting-down-treasury-payments</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 22:49:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>谢恩鲍姆将于周一宣布针对关税的措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/mexico-s-sheinbaum-to-inform-measures-against-us-tariffs-monday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·希因鲍姆表示，她将于周一早上宣布墨西哥政府为抵御美国关税而制定的“ B 计划”的细节。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/mexico-s-sheinbaum-to-inform-measures-against-us-tariffs-monday</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 20:49:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢比奥会见总统后巴拿马向美国做出让步</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/rubio-calls-chinese-influence-over-panama-canal-unacceptable</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国国务卿马尔科·卢比奥周日访问中国期间对巴拿马政府进行猛烈批评后，巴拿马承诺让美国军舰自由通过巴拿马运河，并表示将退出中国签署的贷款计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/rubio-calls-chinese-influence-over-panama-canal-unacceptable</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 19:39:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>与马斯克的 DOGE 团队发生冲突后，美国国际开发署高级职员休假</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/usaid-website-goes-dark-with-future-of-us-assistance-in-doubt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，美国国际开发署的高级安全人员因拒绝让埃隆·马斯克的 DOGE 团队访问机密系统而被停职，救援机构的运作似乎基本陷入瘫痪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/usaid-website-goes-dark-with-future-of-us-assistance-in-doubt</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 09:24:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普瞄准漏洞 Temu，Shein 曾利用其对抗亚马逊</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/trump-tariffs-target-loophole-used-by-chinese-online-retailers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对中国、加拿大和墨西哥征收的新贸易税包括对国际电子商务的猛烈攻击，显然是计划取消长期以来对价值低于 800 美元的包裹的关税豁免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/trump-tariffs-target-loophole-used-by-chinese-online-retailers</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 04:15:36 GMT</pubDate>
